name: F(X)yz
body:
### Welcome to F(X)yz
F(X)yz is a new JavaFX 3D library that provides additional primitives, composite objects, controls and data visualizations that the base JavaFX 8 3D packages do not have.

We (and by we I mean me) have just fired up the first GitHub Page here so clearly we have some work to do.
Until I get some more time, you can see early screenshot previews over at our tumblr:

[F(X)yz Tumblr Preview](http://f-x-yz.tumblr.com/)

[Sometimes I use Google Plus](https://plus.google.com/+SeanPhillipsIsBirdasaur/about) (because I like being alone sometimes)


### Authors and Contributors
@Birdasaur (Sean Phillips) can be found on twitter at @seanmiphillips.
